# Drizzle and D1 (`@core-labs/db`)

## Schema

- Table definitions live under `packages/db/src/schema/`.
- Export inferred types (`$inferSelect`, `$inferInsert`) for repositories and services.

## Client

- Use `createDb(d1)` from `client.ts` inside Workers; pass `D1Database` from `env.DB` (or equivalent binding).

## Migrations

- Generated SQL or Drizzle metadata under `packages/db/src/migrations` (per `drizzle.config.ts`).
- Run `drizzle-kit` with pinned versions; validate `dialect` / `driver` options against installed `drizzle-kit` — APIs change between minors.

## Boundaries

- Repositories perform queries; services choose transactions and orchestrate multiple repositories when needed.
